Former No. 1 Draft Selection Alex Smith Re-Signs With San Francisco 49ers

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-07-29T22:53:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-29/former-no-1-draft-selection-alex-smith-re-signs-with-san-francisco-49ers.html
Quarterback  Alex Smith , the top
overall pick in the 2005 National Football League draft, signed
a one-year deal to return to the San Francisco 49ers, the team
said today.  Smith, who is in his seventh NFL season, made 10 starts for
the 49ers last season.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Gloster at 
 rgloster@bloomberg.net  